data.text: @RSballs It does not describe itself as a fake news site . . . and no one sharing the content is in on the joke. Read the comments. People believe this. No one is laughing.
@DarrenLinvill 😂 This is an absolutely fake news site. "Actual story circulating on social media." What a clown.
@DarrenLinvill They’re really putting their back into it with the purple prose.

@plwarre This website is full of many such shocking claims. Apparently the marines (why the marines?) recently arrested Sotomayor for taking bribes and U.S. Special Forces have taken control of the U.S. oil reserve after Biden gave 5% of it away . . . TO FRANCE?!?
@DarrenLinvill "Why should I change my name? He's the one who sucks."

Real quote: "Valiant Spetznas searching for an alleged bioweapons laboratory in central Ukraine accidently stumble upon a child trafficking den, a dimly lit bunker holding 100 young boys and girls whose eyes dilate when the soldiers’ flashlights illuminate the decrepit chamber."
